{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":669,"text":"This is a talk about sugar and cancer."},{"time":3889,"text":"I became interested in sugar\nwhen I was in college."},{"time":7190,"text":"Not this kind of sugar."},{"time":9066,"text":"It was the sugar that our biology\nprofessors taught us about"},{"time":14041,"text":"in the context of the coating\nof your cells."},{"time":18733,"text":"Maybe you didn't know that your cells\nare coated with sugar."},{"time":22867,"text":"And I didn't know that, either,"},{"time":24466,"text":"until I took these courses in college,"},{"time":26645,"text":"but back then --"},{"time":28081,"text":"and this was in, let's just\ncall it the 1980s --"},{"time":32560,"text":"people didn't know much about why\nour cells are coated with sugar."},{"time":36838,"text":"And when I dug through my notes,\nwhat I noticed I had written down"},{"time":40829,"text":"is that the sugar coating on our cells\nis like the sugar coating"},{"time":45398,"text":"on a peanut M and M."},{"time":47198,"text":"And people thought\nthe sugar coating on our cells"},{"time":50888,"text":"was like a protective coating"},{"time":52742,"text":"that somehow made our cells\nstronger or tougher."}]},{"cues":[{"time":56934,"text":"But we now know, many decades later,"},{"time":59084,"text":"that it's much more complicated than that,"},{"time":61906,"text":"and that the sugars on our cells\nare actually very complex."},{"time":67183,"text":"And if you could shrink yourself down\nto a little miniature airplane"},{"time":72719,"text":"and fly right along\nthe surface of your cells,"},{"time":76525,"text":"it might look something like this --"},{"time":78915,"text":"with geographical features."},{"time":81140,"text":"And now, the complex sugars\nare these trees and bushes --"},{"time":85194,"text":"weeping willows that are\nswaying in the wind"},{"time":87750,"text":"and moving with the waves."},{"time":89811,"text":"And when I started thinking about\nall these complex sugars"},{"time":93648,"text":"that are like this foliage on our cells,"},{"time":96598,"text":"it became one of the most interesting\nproblems that I encountered"},{"time":99739,"text":"as a biologist and also as a chemist."},{"time":103657,"text":"And so now we tend\nto think about the sugars"},{"time":106616,"text":"that are populating\nthe surface of our cells"},{"time":109908,"text":"as a language."},{"time":112342,"text":"They have a lot of information\nstored in their complex structures."}]},{"cues":[{"time":117142,"text":"But what are they trying to tell us?"},{"time":120548,"text":"I can tell you that we do know\nsome information"},{"time":123887,"text":"that comes from these sugars,"},{"time":125516,"text":"and it's turned out already\nto be incredibly important"},{"time":128475,"text":"in the world of medicine."}]},{"cues":[{"time":130777,"text":"For example, one thing\nyour sugars are telling us"},{"time":134462,"text":"is your blood type."},{"time":137041,"text":"So your blood cells, your red blood\ncells, are coated with sugars,"},{"time":141219,"text":"and the chemical structures of those\nsugars determine your blood type."},{"time":145920,"text":"So for example, I know\nthat I am blood type O."},{"time":149867,"text":"How many people are also blood type O?"},{"time":153002,"text":"Put your hands up."},{"time":154184,"text":"It's a pretty common one,"},{"time":155401,"text":"so when so few hands go up,\neither you're not paying attention"},{"time":158360,"text":"or you don't know your blood type,\nand both of those are bad."}]},{"cues":[{"time":161274,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":162313,"text":"But for those of you who share\nthe blood type O with me,"},{"time":165000,"text":"what this means is that we have\nthis chemical structure"},{"time":167739,"text":"on the surface of our blood cells:"},{"time":170296,"text":"three simple sugars linked together\nto make a more complex sugar."},{"time":174043,"text":"And that, by definition, is blood type O."}]},{"cues":[{"time":177366,"text":"Now, how many people are blood type A?"},{"time":180574,"text":"Right here."},{"time":181767,"text":"That means you have\nan enzyme in your cells"},{"time":184752,"text":"that adds one more building block,"},{"time":187192,"text":"that red sugar,"},{"time":188591,"text":"to build a more complex structure."},{"time":191116,"text":"And how many people are blood type B?"},{"time":194298,"text":"Quite a few."},{"time":195487,"text":"You have a slightly different enzyme\nthan the A people,"},{"time":198239,"text":"so you build a slightly\ndifferent structure,"},{"time":200379,"text":"and those of you that are AB"},{"time":202516,"text":"have the enzyme from your mother,\nthe other enzyme from your father,"},{"time":205732,"text":"and now you make both of these structures\nin roughly equal proportions."},{"time":209531,"text":"And when this was figured out,"},{"time":211959,"text":"which is now back in the previous century,"},{"time":214721,"text":"this enabled one of the most important\nmedical procedures in the world,"},{"time":218262,"text":"which, of course,\nis the blood transfusion."},{"time":220664,"text":"And by knowing what your blood type is,"},{"time":222584,"text":"we can make sure,\nif you ever need a transfusion,"},{"time":225200,"text":"that your donor has the same blood type,"},{"time":227745,"text":"so that your body\ndoesn't see foreign sugars,"},{"time":231783,"text":"which it wouldn't like\nand would certainly reject."}]},{"cues":[{"time":236113,"text":"What else are the sugars on the surface\nof your cells trying to tell us?"},{"time":241112,"text":"Well, those sugars might be telling us\nthat you have cancer."},{"time":246708,"text":"So a few decades ago,"},{"time":248984,"text":"correlations began to emerge\nfrom the analysis of tumor tissue."},{"time":254401,"text":"And the typical scenario is a patient\nwould have a tumor detected,"},{"time":258936,"text":"and the tissue would be removed\nin a biopsy procedure"},{"time":262788,"text":"and then sent down to a pathology lab"},{"time":265582,"text":"where that tissue would be analyzed\nto look for chemical changes"},{"time":269737,"text":"that might inform the oncologist\nabout the best course of treatment."},{"time":274979,"text":"And what was discovered\nfrom studies like that"},{"time":277887,"text":"is that the sugars have changed"},{"time":280775,"text":"when the cell transforms\nfrom being healthy to being sick."},{"time":286823,"text":"And those correlations have come up\nagain and again and again."},{"time":292497,"text":"But a big question in the field\nhas been: Why?"},{"time":296987,"text":"Why do cancers have different sugars?\nWhat's the importance of that?"},{"time":301255,"text":"Why does it happen, and what\ncan we do about it if it does turn out"},{"time":304640,"text":"to be related to the disease process?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":309783,"text":"So, one of the changes that we study"},{"time":313018,"text":"is an increase in the density\nof a particular sugar"},{"time":318587,"text":"that's called sialic acid."},{"time":321617,"text":"And I think this is going to be\none of the most important sugars"},{"time":325565,"text":"of our times,"},{"time":326747,"text":"so I would encourage everybody\nto get familiar with this word."},{"time":331502,"text":"Sialic acid is not\nthe kind of sugar that we eat."},{"time":334491,"text":"Those are different sugars."},{"time":336602,"text":"This is a kind of sugar\nthat is actually found"},{"time":339590,"text":"at certain levels on all\nof the cells in your body."},{"time":342742,"text":"It's actually quite common on your cells."},{"time":346393,"text":"But for some reason,"},{"time":348451,"text":"cancer cells, at least in a successful,\nprogressive disease,"},{"time":353963,"text":"tend to have more sialic acid"},{"time":357096,"text":"than a normal, healthy cell would have."},{"time":359467,"text":"And why?"},{"time":360933,"text":"What does that mean?"},{"time":363276,"text":"Well, what we've learned"},{"time":364752,"text":"is that it has to do\nwith your immune system."}]},{"cues":[{"time":368935,"text":"So let me tell you a little bit\nabout the importance of your immune system"},{"time":372525,"text":"in cancer."},{"time":373713,"text":"And this is something that's, I think,\nin the news a lot these days."},{"time":377255,"text":"You know, people are starting\nto become familiar with the term"},{"time":380185,"text":"\"cancer immune therapy.\""},{"time":382971,"text":"And some of you might even know people"},{"time":384806,"text":"who are benefiting from these very new\nways of treating cancer."},{"time":389848,"text":"What we now know\nis that your immune cells,"},{"time":393113,"text":"which are the white blood cells\ncoursing through your bloodstream,"},{"time":397071,"text":"protect you on a daily basis\nfrom things gone bad --"},{"time":401751,"text":"including cancer."},{"time":403951,"text":"And so in this picture,"},{"time":405966,"text":"those little green balls\nare your immune cells,"},{"time":408711,"text":"and that big pink cell is a cancer cell."},{"time":412250,"text":"And these immune cells go around\nand taste all the cells in your body."},{"time":417039,"text":"That's their job."},{"time":418913,"text":"And most of the time, the cells taste OK."}]},{"cues":[{"time":421692,"text":"But once in a while,\na cell might taste bad."},{"time":424744,"text":"Hopefully, that's the cancer cell,"},{"time":426579,"text":"and when those immune cells\nget the bad taste,"},{"time":428986,"text":"they launch an all-out strike\nand kill those cells."},{"time":432630,"text":"So we know that."},{"time":433807,"text":"We also know that if you can\npotentiate that tasting,"},{"time":438247,"text":"if you can encourage those immune cells\nto actually take a big old bite"},{"time":442099,"text":"out of a cancer cell,"},{"time":443366,"text":"you get a better job protecting\nyourself from cancer every day"},{"time":446981,"text":"and maybe even curing a cancer."},{"time":449509,"text":"And there are now a couple of drugs\nout there in the market"},{"time":452379,"text":"that are used to treat cancer patients"},{"time":454474,"text":"that act exactly by this process."},{"time":457726,"text":"They activate the immune system"},{"time":459379,"text":"so that the immune system\ncan be more vigorous"},{"time":462150,"text":"in protecting us from cancer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":463926,"text":"In fact, one of those drugs"},{"time":465993,"text":"may well have spared\nPresident Jimmy Carter's life."},{"time":469516,"text":"Do you remember, President Carter\nhad malignant melanoma"},{"time":474020,"text":"that had metastasized to his brain,"},{"time":476902,"text":"and that diagnosis is one\nthat is usually accompanied by numbers"},{"time":480280,"text":"like \"months to live.\""},{"time":483093,"text":"But he was treated with one\nof these new immune-stimulating drugs,"},{"time":487512,"text":"and now his melanoma\nappears to be in remission,"},{"time":490895,"text":"which is remarkable,"},{"time":492560,"text":"considering the situation\nonly a few years ago."},{"time":496025,"text":"In fact, it's so remarkable"},{"time":497869,"text":"that provocative statements like this one:"},{"time":500693,"text":"\"Cancer is having a penicillin moment,\"\npeople are saying,"},{"time":504432,"text":"with these new immune therapy drugs."},{"time":506277,"text":"I mean, that's an incredibly bold thing\nto say about a disease"},{"time":509499,"text":"which we've been fighting for a long time"},{"time":512172,"text":"and mostly losing the battle with."},{"time":514855,"text":"So this is very exciting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":516907,"text":"Now what does this have to do with sugars?"},{"time":519343,"text":"Well, I'll tell you what we've learned."},{"time":522944,"text":"When an immune cell snuggles\nup against a cancer cell to take a taste,"},{"time":529304,"text":"it's looking for signs of disease,"},{"time":531977,"text":"and if it finds those signs,"},{"time":533920,"text":"the cell gets activated and it launches\na missile strike and kills the cell."},{"time":539269,"text":"But if that cancer cell has a dense forest\nof that sugar, sialic acid,"},{"time":545731,"text":"well, it starts to taste pretty good."},{"time":549507,"text":"And there's a protein on immune cells\nthat grabs the sialic acid,"},{"time":554175,"text":"and if that protein\ngets held at that synapse"},{"time":558000,"text":"between the immune cell\nand the cancer cell,"},{"time":561171,"text":"it puts that immune cell to sleep."},{"time":563809,"text":"The sialic acids are telling\nthe immune cell,"},{"time":567135,"text":"\"Hey, this cell's all right.\nNothing to see here, move along."},{"time":570360,"text":"Look somewhere else.\""},{"time":572741,"text":"So in other words,"},{"time":573987,"text":"as long as our cells are wearing\na thick coat of sialic acid,"},{"time":579399,"text":"they look fabulous, right?"},{"time":582036,"text":"It's amazing."},{"time":584524,"text":"And what if you could strip off that coat"},{"time":587702,"text":"and take that sugar away?"},{"time":590024,"text":"Well, your immune system"},{"time":593047,"text":"might be able to see that cancer cell\nfor what it really is:"},{"time":597272,"text":"something that needs to be destroyed."}]},{"cues":[{"time":600875,"text":"And so this is what we're doing in my lab."},{"time":603704,"text":"We're developing new medicines"},{"time":606050,"text":"that are basically\ncell-surface lawnmowers --"},{"time":609861,"text":"molecules that go down\nto the surface of these cancer cells"},{"time":613538,"text":"and just cut off those sialic acids,"},{"time":616427,"text":"so that the immune system\ncan reach its full potential"},{"time":620756,"text":"in eliminating those cancer\ncells from our body."}]},{"cues":[{"time":624983,"text":"So in closing,"},{"time":627819,"text":"let me just remind you again:"},{"time":629996,"text":"your cells are coated with sugars."},{"time":632972,"text":"The sugars are telling cells\naround that cell"},{"time":637691,"text":"whether the cell is good or bad."},{"time":640682,"text":"And that's important,"},{"time":641871,"text":"because our immune system needs\nto leave the good cells alone."},{"time":644951,"text":"Otherwise, we'd have autoimmune diseases."},{"time":648315,"text":"But once in a while,\ncancers get the ability"},{"time":651487,"text":"to express these new sugars."},{"time":653067,"text":"And now that we understand"},{"time":654423,"text":"how those sugars mesmerize\nthe immune system,"},{"time":657607,"text":"we can come up with new medicines\nto wake up those immune cells,"},{"time":661816,"text":"tell them, \"Ignore\nthe sugars, eat the cell"},{"time":665067,"text":"and have a delicious snack, on cancer.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":668574,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":670073,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}